<h1><img height="280" src="Images/communication/resources/hover-always-2.png" style="float: left;" width="162" />KBYR 91.5 FM - Always Inspirational</h1>
<p>KBYR is part of the broadcasting network of Brigham Young University-Idaho. With an inspirational format, KBYR serves the campus and Rexburg community with programming 24/7. A pleasant mix of over 2800 songs can be heard with Devotionals, General Conference reports, talks from Education Week, and various symposia sponsored by BYU and BYU-Idaho. Programming is shaped and governed by a team of students representing academic areas including Communications and Music. KBYR offers a safe haven where listeners can feel comfortable with uplifting music and messages of hope and inspiration.</p>
